title: CBB's Jamie O'Hara confirms he's moved on from Bianca Gascoigne with ex-girlfriend Elizabeth-Jayne Tierney
text:
Bianca Gascoigne gets tearful about Jamie O'Hara Share this video Watch Next 
They had been a close couple before splitting; in May 2016, Jamie took to Instagram to gush about his partner, writing: “The absolute love of my life, gives me the strength to get through anything and don't appreciate her enough sometimes @elizabethjayneinsta through thick and thin.” 
And Elizabeth-Jayne repaid the compliments in her own Instagram post, writing: “I’ve always stayed so classy and dignified over any current situation he is in, like any wife or girlfriend should. I would never sell him or anyone out for a financial gain. 
“But like any loving doting partner I will protect my love till the end. Because isn’t that love? Protect, love and secure each other. We have our disagreements. Never about anything other then trying to persist in a relationship were so madly in love with but find it hard. They dated last year (Photo: FameFlynet) Jamie also shared this Snapchat (Photo: Snapchat) 
"I’m so glad we get to spend some time together other then juggling everything we deal with like normal day to day people plus a little bit more drama, nice I get to remember why we keep fighting. 
“The love will always always remain weather we last a life time a long time or a little time. And that is the beauty of what no one or anything can take away!” 
Jamie split from Elizabeth-Jayne eight months ago, with the model telling The Sun in January: “Me and Jamie have not been together for eight or nine months. He is there [CBB] for nothing to do with me and not my problem.” Jamie and Bianca in the CBB house (Photo: Supplied by WENN) Jamie and Bianca were very close Video Loading Click to play Tap to play The video will start in 8 Cancel Play now
